{
  "texts": [
    "The quality of the text produced by these systems varies significantly, even when using very informative prompts.",
    "Presently, these tools may be more beneficial for master's students who are required to write brief essays rather than for researchers.",
    "Nonetheless, as the technology continues to evolve, it is anticipated that a new generation of tools will emerge, offering substantial assistance in academic writing.",
    "These AI systems could potentially automate several complex tasks, such as generating comprehensive literature reviews (Hope et al. 2023), recommending citations (Ali et al. 2020; Buscaldi et al. 2024), and identifying new scientific hypotheses (Sybrandt et al. 2020; Borrego et al. 2022).",
    "In this survey, we performed an extensive analysis of SLR tools, with a particular focus on the integration of AI technologies in the screening and extraction phases."
  ]
}